DSB Stadion is a multi - use stadium in Alkmaar , Netherlands . It is currently used mostly for football matches and is the home stadium of AZ . The stadium is able to hold 17,023 people and it officially opened on 4 August 2006 with a friendly against Arsenal . AZ lost the match 3 - 0 , with Gilberto Silva scoring the stadium 's first ever goal . DSB Stadion replaces the club 's former ground , Alkmaarder Hout . The main stand is called Victorie Tribune , the stand with the fanatic supporters is called Van der Ben Tribune ( Ben - Side ) , the stand behind the other goal is called Westzijde , and the stand opposite to the main stand is called Molenaar Tribune . The official name is DSB Stadion , but some supporters call it Victorie Stadion , a name that alludes to a victory over Spain during the Eighty Years ' War . 